1 AN ACT
2 To enact R.S. 37:22.1, relative to artificial intelligence; to require a healthcare professional
3 to disclose to a patient the use of certain software; and to provide for related matters.
4 Be it enacted by the Legislature of Louisiana:
5 Section 1. R.S. 37:22.1 is hereby enacted to read as follows:
6 §22.1. Recordings; artificial intelligence; disclosure
7 A healthcare professional licensed by this Title shall verbally disclose the use
8 of any recording device, software, or service to a patient before recording any part
9 of an appointment or treatment to be transcribed by artificial intelligence.
