HB 475 Engrossed 2026 Regular Session Berault
Abstract: Requires a healthcare professional to disclose to a patient the use of a recording
device, software, or service to transcribe using artificial intelligence during an
appointment or treatment.
Proposed law requires a healthcare professional licensed under present law to disclose to a
patient, prior to an appointment or treatment, the use of any recording device, software, or
service that utilizes artificial intelligence to transcribe communications between the
professional and the patient.
(Adds R.S. 37:22.1)
